Create Shark Groups 11

Step 1. Create Shark groups.

a. Right click on SpeciesAll column and select new group, follow the GIF Below to

    create the groups (I created two groups so that you can see the process).


b. To select multiple, press Ctrl and click on the Shark Name from the list then click

     on Groups, rename the group and press enter to create group.



Step 2. Use these Screen shots and the Gif below to create the rest of the groups. They contain the group name and their components. Click OK when you done to save the groups that you have created.








Creating Groups in power bi:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yK0JBwN_9o0
